      • StatePortProvider

        public StatePortProvider(ISSRExecutor ssrExecutor,
                         ISunriseConnection sunriseConnection,
                         String controller)
        Creates a new StatePortProvider for the given controller. After creation, collectStatePortData() must be called to initialize the complete list of state ports.
        Parameters:
        ssrExecutor - ISSRExecutor to send SSRs to the controller.
        sunriseConnection - sunrise connection used at state port events.
        controller - name of the controller
